                     <decoNote xml:id="d1" type="drawing">
                        <locus target="#11r"/>
                        <desc>A drawing of <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin and Child</ref> with two <term key="angel" ana="#angel">angels</term> in pencil and violet ink. The leaf has an oval form. On the
  <locus target="#11v"/> it is written <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለዛቲ፡ ስዕል፡ ሰአሊሃ፡ አለቃ፡ <persName role="illustrator" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12668GabraI">ገብረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</persName>
                           </foreign>.</desc>

